system.description: When you tap into the gossip and rumor of the celebrity industry for information on an important city figure, roll + Superior.

failure.label: Complications...
failure.value: Ask one anyway, but they hear about your interest in them.

partial.label: Partial success
partial.value:
Ask one.

  • What are they up to?
  • What or who do they most care about?
  • What allies do they have? Enemies?
  • Where and when can I find them?
  • How could I make them vulnerable to me?

success.label: Success!
success.value:
Ask three.

  • What are they up to?
  • What or who do they most care about?
  • What allies do they have? Enemies?
  • Where and when can I find them?
  • How could I make them vulnerable to me?
